h2. IRC

You can hang out on IRC with other Karaf developers and users.

If you are using Mozilla you can just click on the IRC link

* [#karaf at irc.codehaus.org|irc://irc.codehaus.org/karaf] 


h3. Using an IRC client

Here are the connection details. For an IRC client we recommend [XChat|http://www.xchat.org/] or [XChatAqua|http://xchataqua.sourceforge.net/] on OS X

